title: 35.01 DEFINITIONS.
text:
Unless the language or context clearly indicates that a different meaning is intended, the words defined in this section as used in this chapter have the meanings given them.
"Board" or "state board" means the Board of Animal Health.
MS 1978 [Repealed, 1980 c 467 s 44]
"Livestock" and "domestic animals" include poultry.
